ravel about looking for an open parking spot.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Pollution Reduction:</strong> Searching for an available parking place consumes much too much car oil, petrol, diesel, CNG, etc. in a single day. An optimal parking solution will significantly save travel time, minimizing the quantity of daily vehicle exhaust and, eventually, India’s and the global ecological footprint.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Improved User Experience: </strong>A digital parking solution will combine all aspects of the user experience into a single operation. Driver payment, location search, time notifications, and spot identification are all seamlessly integrated into the destination arrival procedure.</li>\r\n <li><strong>New Revenue Streams:</strong> Individuals, businesses and other institutions can rent out their spaces and earn a passive income.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Easy Integrated Payments</strong>: Invoicing & Payments are collected and given through the ‘ParkingAdda’ application. This could also maintain transparency of accounts between customers and vendors with the company.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Increased Employment Cost</strong>: With this smart parking system, several new revenue streams are possible. For example, we would be having parking lot representatives, this will increase the employment India, in these job scarce times of Covid-19.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><strong>Vehicle Security:</strong> - Our spot representative have access to real-time parking lot data, which may aid in the prevention of suspicious behavior and parking infractions.<strong> </strong>Furthermore, less spot-searching traffic on the highways might minimize accidents caused by the impediment of looking for parking.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><strong>Space Safety and Security: </strong>Users can only use our parking spots for registered vehicles also our spot representative will be available to detect any suspicious behavior and parking infractions.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><strong>Real-Time Data and Trend Insight</strong>: A digital parking system may gradually generate data that reveals trends and relationships between parking lots and users. These patterns may prove to be invaluable to parking lot owners in terms of how to respond to drivers. Booking confirmation, booking start time reminder, booking end time reminder, payment notification, etc. is send on real time basis especially when you deal with ‘ ParkingAdda ’.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><strong>Enhanced Service and Brand Image:</strong> A pleasant experience may significantly improve the commercial or corporate entity&#39;s brand image in the eyes of the user. Visitors will be amazed by the cutting-edge technology and accessible features, whether the destination is an airport, a corporate company office, a function, event, a wholesale store / shopping houses or.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>As proof of the aforementioned benefits, the use of a digital parking solution via ‘ParkingAdda’ Online Parking application would undoubtedly be a significant investment for any company or government. Even in some of the world&#39;s largest cities, where there are around four parking spaces per car, individuals are still unable to find a place to park their automobiles. As the global population grows and becomes more sophisticated, it is critical to implement a user-friendly and well-planned parking system that can be utilized anywhere in the globe. ParkingAdda in India is a need based solution for the betterment of every citizen and also the environment as a whole. In India, where parking problems account for almost 30% of all traffic delays, such a solution may be revolutionary. ‘Park Like a Boss’ or ‘Enhance Smart Parking’ and be a part of a revolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also Read-</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Parking Issues in Mumbai!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its official