t is totally adaptable. We ParkingAdda works with any form of parking garage or car park, as well as any parking system as long its legal. It can be fully automated using our proprietary parking technology of ParkingAdda or in any other way that meets the demands of your company. Earning from schools or sports ground can be a huge benefit to yours accounts during slack periods. For example, even if you get 5 hours of parking daily for 20 spots you can make a minimum of up to Rs. 1, 50,000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You may now choose how long you wish to hire out your parking place. You may also choose the days and times when your parking will be available and when you will need it. We are happy to advise you on a reasonable rental price based on comparable rentals and parking costs in your area or location. Your space will be safe since we will have a dedicated employee at each location to oversee operations, and all reservations and revenues will be reflected on your app.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits to a Space Renter-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What happens to the parking place when you&#39;re not in it? What happens to wedding grounds during the afternoons? What happens to the grounds of religious spaces, schools and other institutions, etc?  Probably nothing. It seems like a waste to have so much space and then leave it open, when you have an option to earn lakhs through companies like ParkingAdda. Here are some reasons why you should rent out your parking space while you aren&#39;t using it-</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li>But obvious are the earnings-</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>So this one is pretty self-evident. If you rent out your parking space, you can earn a lump sum amount on monthly basis the space usage through us. However, it is still worth discussing because it is perhaps the most significant component. People are prepared to pay a lot for parking, especially in major cities, so why shouldn&#39;t some of that money go to you if you have space