grown at an unexpected rate. We now share automobiles, computers, residences, and a variety of other items. We are increasingly discovering that sharing goods, as well as their resource costs, may be a highly effective way to live. By sharing your parking place, you become a part of a big technological and social revolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Also Read-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Parking Issues in Mumbai! ‘ParkingAdda’ is here to solve parking issues in Mumbai</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its official, very soon Mumbaikar can book parking spaces in advance via the ‘ParkingAdda App’ within minutes. In India, parking spaces are getting increasingly scarce. Surely, we want to find parking spots quickly and in a much simpler way, rather than having to keep an eye out for our automobiles and going from one spot to the next in the hope of finding a parking. &#39;ParkingAdda&#39; is an internet service that assists you in finding a parking spot. Read More..</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>How Drivers Will Benefit from Smart Parking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Smart Parking is now one of the most popular Smart City efforts, and India is no exception, with ParkingAdda introducing itself as a pioneer in Smart Online Parking projects. Soon searching for, ‘parking near me’ will be a norm.</p>\r\n', 1, '19-10-22', '', 'parking'),
(8, '<h1><strong>Save 20 Mins of travel time with Parking Adda</strong></h1>\r\n', 'assets/uploads/Save_20_Mins_of_travel_time_with_Parking_Adda.jpg', '<p>When is the last time you planned your work, meeting or drive for a special occasion, followed the plan to the fullest and reached the destination in time with a positive attitude? In metro and urban cities especially in Mumbai or Delhi it’s still a dream every citizen, a perfect drive plan always has hurdles that one cannot overcome easily, for instance surprise traffic, or if all goes fine no parking. </p>\r\n', '<p>When is the last time you planned your work, meeting or drive for a special occasion, followed the plan to the fullest and reached the destination in time with a positive attitude? In metro and urban cities especially in Mumbai or Delhi it’s still a dream every citizen, a perfect drive plan always has hurdles that one cannot overcome easily, for instance surprise traffic, or if all goes fine no parking. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine arriving at work and daily being able to walk inside your office after driving in less than 5 minutes, in a good mood. The genuine tale, on the other hand, does not follow this pattern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will spend at least 30 - 60 minutes on the road if you self-drive! When there is no traffic, it is a lucky day; yet, if you are stuck in traffic, your entire day is spent agonizing or nagging over the same thing and the same reflects on your work. It does hamper your productivity. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The same goes for when you&#39;re travelling for a family wedding or celebration, you&#39;re exhausted and frustrated by the time you arrive, and on top of that, people will come up to you and ask what took you so long! Isn&#39;t this incredibly relatable?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In today’s day and time with the accuracy of maps and other IoT technologies traffic is something that gets accounted for or can be checked in advance before leaving for a destination. This means that even if you arrive at your business or other function on time or on schedule, you will normally waste more time parking your car because:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>you keep going around your parking lot looking for a parking space</li>\r\n <li>You may or may not be able to locate the parking manager.</li>\r\n <li>When you don&#39;t have enough change, you&#39;ll have to wait longer to pay with cash.</li>\r\n <li>There are some early movers who arrive before you and take your preferred parking spot.</li>\r\n <li>Parking is not allowed in the locality for outsiders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Oh, that’s really tough to add to a work day, especially on a client meeting day (Lawyers, Chartered Accountants, etc. ParkingAdda has understood these difficulties are provider smart solutions to not only counter these solutions but also other problems like fuel wastage, vehicle safety, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Time Saver-</strong> Additionally, by driving fewer kilometer’s in quest of a parking spot, you will save time that may be better spent on work, relaxation, or hobbies. You will save money on gasoline as a result.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Spend less money-</strong> It goes without saying that driving more efficiently while seeking for a parking spot will save you money on gas. You will save money on gasoline as a result. If you know your location has a parking spot and you can book it ahead of time, it encourages you to drive your own car instead of hiring an Ola or Uber cab. Most of the time, it is less expensive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Increased security-</strong> Because drivers know where they can park, they are less distracted when hunting for a parking spot. They&#39;ll be entirely focused on the journey. They may reduce accidents and improve safety for themselves, their own automobiles, other cars, and pedestrians by keeping their eyes on the road.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Map will guide you to your spot-</strong> If you are not visiting a specific (area of a) city because you do not want to deal with the hassle of finding a parking spot, the ParkingAdda mobile app can assist you in doing so by allowing you to choose and book an open spot in that location up to 36 hours in advance or after reaching the destination use ‘Parking Near Me’ feature. It can be frustrating to know you&#39;ll be driving for a long time and will most likely wind up somewhere far, far away from your destination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vehicle Safety-</strong> Smart parking with ParkingAdda will not only direct you to your parking site using a MAP, but we also have a dedicated person at each location to ensure vehicle safety and provide additional information or guidance on call.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A driver will receive Real-Time Updates on spot availability and reservations – </strong>He&#39;ll get alerts 15 minutes before his parking time begins (in the event of pre-booked parking) and 15 minutes before it ends, providing him the option to extend his parking time via the app.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Minimizing one&#39;s personal environmental footprint-</strong> Driving fewer kilometers to obtain a parking spot has the added benefit of reducing individual emissions. All fossil fuels, gasoline, diesel, and the majority of alternative fuels produce emissions, especially carbon dioxide (Co2). There will be no direct influence on human life from these contaminants. Despite this, CO2 is the most significant contributor to greenhouse gas emissions and, as a result, climate change.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>A few related facts-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Due to the large number of automobiles, Mumbai is one of India&#39;s most congested cities (about 34 lakh vehicles registered till 2019 )</li>\r\n <li>The average Mumbaikar spends 11 days per year stuck in traffic.</li>\r\n <li>The rising number of cars on the road does not correspond to the available parking spaces in cities.</li>\r\n <li>Commuters squander a full week in traffic each year</li>\r\n <li>Americans spend $73 billion a year looking for parking</li>\r\n <li>India constructed over 4 million of the 70.47 million passenger automobiles produced globally in 2018.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What you need to do to save time with ParkingAdda?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>You can get the ParkingAdda Mobile App from the Google Play Store or the Apple App Store.</li>\r\n <li>You may search nearby parking (parking near me based on current location) or pre-book parking at a distant location using the app.</li>\r\n <li>Parking places will be accessible in real time based on your search location on the app (Current status of the spot whether booked, Not available or available)</li>\r\n <li>You can reserve it as soon as you see it available.</li>\r\n <li>Payment must be made digitally through the ParkingAdda app wallet. Read the Cancellation Policies for more information on this money being refundable.</li>\r\n <li>Following your reservation, you will receive a map that will direct you to your parking location, as well as the contact information for a dedicated representative in case you have any further questions.</li>\r\n <li>Invoice or challan will be digitally available on the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>With us you’ll save 20 mins daily, 5 days a year and further you can do the math. No more questing for parking, no traffic congestions due to illegal parking and embrace digital payments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also share your vacant parking spot and earn with ParkingAdda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also Read-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rent your Parking Space to Smart Parking Solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The consequences of vehicular pollution on human health in urban India</p>\r\n', 1, '19-10-22', '', 'parking'),
(9, '<h1><strong>The consequences of vehicular pollution on human health in urban India</strong></h1>\r\n', 'assets/uploads/The_consequences_of_vehicular_pollution_on_human_health_in_urban_India.jpg', '<p>The fast growth of urban India has resulted in a massive increase in the number of automobiles on the road. This has doubled in certain cities during the last decade. In recent years, rapid urbanization and the expansion of motor vehicles have had a significant impact on human life and the environment. Automobiles are a major cause of urban air pollution and are becoming a larger source of anthropogenic carbon dioxide and other greenhouse gases. The transportation industry is a key contributor, accounting for 90% of total emissions.</p>\r\n', '<p>The fast growth of urban India has resulted in a massive increase in the number of automobiles on the road. This has doubled in certain cities during the last decade. In recent years, rapid urbanization and the expansion of motor vehicles have had a significant impact on human life and the environment. Automobiles are a major cause of urban air pollution and are becoming a larger source of anthropogenic carbon dioxide and other greenhouse gases. The transportation industry is a key contributor, accounting for 90% of total emissions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Air pollution is a severe threat to human health in the environment. Nausea, difficulty breathing, skin irritations, birth abnormalities, immunosuppression, and cancer are just a few of the side effects. All of these circumstances show that air pollution is becoming a serious issue in India, and that there is an urgent need to create a healthy atmosphere and raise the level of research globally. The current study examines the rise in vehicle pollution in India and its impact on human health as a result of increased road traffic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In major cities, the contribution of various sectors to ambient air quality mainly are domestic sector 8 %, industrial sector around 20 % and vehicular emission around 72 %.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>‘In India, there are an estimated 300 million automobiles’</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&#39;There are an estimated 300 million automobiles in India.&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Over the last five years, the number of tiny dangerous particles in Mumbai&#39;s automobile traffic has nearly doubled, making it the city&#39;s biggest contributor to the city&#39;s already poor air quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to a research conducted by the System of Air Quality Weather Forecasting and Research (SAFAR), the transportation sector accounted for 30.5 percent of PM 2.5 emissions in 2019-20, up to 16 percent in 2016-17.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to SAFAR, industry and power plants contributed 18 percent of PM2.5 emissions in 2019-20, down to 36 percent in 2016-17.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the same way, municipal garbage contributes 21.5 percent in 2019–20.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Solid waste plants, open burnings, crematoriums, the aviation sector, brick kilns, and other municipal waste contributors are among them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Home burnings, which include residential cooking, emissions from street sellers, and wood burning, have decreased from 27% in 2016-17 to 15% in 2019-20.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to Dr. Gufran Beig source taken from TOI article, senior scientist and founder project director of SAFAR, the change was caused by a combination of increased vehicle traffic in Mumbai and more stalling at traffic signals, resulting in traffic congestion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A need based step taken by ParkingAdda to try and better the vehicle traffic </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online parking is one of the fastest growing and most widely used Smart City Solutions in the world. Universities, airports, public garages, and shopping malls are just a few of the businesses that have begun to reap the benefits of automated/smart parking technology through the usage of various Digital Parking applications. The ability to connect, analyze, and automate data collected from gadgets, referred to as and powered by the Internet of Things, has made this modern parking system possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>“4 wheeler density on the streets of Mumbai was around 12 lakhs in 2020, an overall surge of 30% in total number of vehicles is expected by 2025”. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>In India, ‘ParkingAdda’ is one of the first movers in the market to introduce convenient online parking solutions, which any individual can reap benefits from. We have developed our own proprietary technology and have manufactured our sensors in-house, we are a ‘Make In India’ initiative. Our IOT-based smart parking management system enables parking operators to utilize parking resources more efficiently while also providing drivers with simplicity of use. Drivers can identify parking spots sooner with an effective parking management solution, which cuts fuel costs, saves time, and, most importantly, minimizes irritation. Because Parking Management solutions not only assists you to identify vacant spots faster, it also guides you to your exact parking spot through Maps. One of the stand-out USP of ParkingAdda is that every parking location will have representative you can contact after booking, for any additional guidance. Sensor installations and dedicated parking representatives gives a trust feeling of vehicle and space safety. Better and easy app usage increases authorized car park occupancy and also income to space renters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The digital parking system from ParkingAdda uses real-time data, apps, and accurate sensors to show users which parking spaces are available and which are not. The idea is to cut down on time spent physically looking for a suitable parking lot, space, or even floor. Some systems may offer a comprehensive set of services, including parking time notifications, online payments, and even car-finding capabilities for larger parking lots. In terms of environment friendly issues we ParkingAdda provides the below solutions-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Parking optimization: Users can use the app to discover the best available parking spot, saving them time, effort, and money. The parking lot soon fills up, and businesses and commercial organizations can take advantage of the available space. Unauthorized parking and on-street parking can both be reduced.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Improved Traffic Flow: As fewer cars are required to go about looking for an open parking spot and roadside parking can be reduced, traffic flow improves.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Pollution reduction: Looking for a parking spot uses far too much automobile oil, gasoline, diesel, CNG, and other fuels in a single day. An ideal parking solution will greatly reduce travel time while also reducing the amount of daily car exhaust and, as a result, India&#39;s and the world&#39;s pollution levels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Simple Integrated and Paperless Payments: The &#39;ParkingAdda&#39; application collects and distributes invoicing and payments. This reduces use of paper challans and receipts and also helps the organization maintain account transparency between customers and vendors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>For Detailed Features Also Read-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How Drivers Will Benefit from Smart Parking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rent your Parking Space to Smart Parking Solutions</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>As evidence of the aforementioned advantages, any organization or government would surely benefit from the usage of a digital parking solution such as the &#39;ParkingAdda&#39; Digital Parking app. Individuals are still unable to locate a parking space in some of the world&#39;s largest cities, where there are approximately four parking spaces per car. As the world&#39;s population grows and gets more sophisticated, it&#39;s more important than ever to put in place a user-friendly and well-planned parking system that can be used anywhere. In India, a ParkingAdda is a need-based solution for the benefit of all citizens as well as the environment as a whole.</p>\r\n', 1, '19-10-22', '', 'parking'),
(10, '<h1><strong>What are the issues faced in parking lots? </strong></h1>\r\n', 'assets/uploads/What_are_the_issues_faced_in_parking_lots.jpg', '<p>Distraction is a common cause of parking lot injuries. Parking lots are more dangerous than you would believe. Every year, tens of thousands of accidents occur in parking lots and garages, resulting in around hundreds of deaths and thousands of injuries. Parking lots become even more perilous around the holidays.</p>\r\n', '<p>Distraction is a common cause of parking lot injuries. Parking lots are more dangerous than you would believe. Every year, tens of thousands of accidents occur in parking lots and garages, resulting in around hundreds of deaths and thousands of injuries. Parking lots become even more perilous around the holidays.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Parking lots are made for automobiles, not pedestrians. Parking lots should be treated as roadways and crossroads, complete with speed restrictions, traffic markings, and traffic patterns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to auto insurance, the number of claims spikes on Black Friday Sales and continues to be higher than usual throughout the holiday shopping season. Many fender-benders go unreported, therefore the number of events is likely larger than insurance claims imply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A few common vehicle parking issues are due to no proper parking guide, driving through different streets / levels of parking lots in search of parking, tire inflation, other vehicles park close to your vehicle obstructing movements, identifying your car park at the time of moving out results in time wastage, etc. Indians face a tough time driving especially in metro cities due to traffic & parking issues. The major reasons for the same is, ‘number of vehicles has out beaten the number of parking spaces’, due to these a lot of car owners park illegally on streets or any other place that they find vacant. By parking illegally the consequences are to be bared not only by the other citizen including road officials but also by the same person who has parked illegally (toeing vans, other damages and expenses). The only gainer is the Government who generates income in terms ‘challans’, etc. These are a common phenomenon in countries like India and in order to address these issues ‘ParkingAdda’ online parking app has tried to find a few parking solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Addressing the Indian market ParkingAdda has introduced a parking guide as a part of their service, who will be available 24x7, to guide the car owner as well as assure vehicle safety. So for example- When you book a parking spot online through the ParkingAdda android parking app or the IOS parking app, the map will guide you to your booked parking spot and also in case of any connectivity issues or other issues, have an option to call the ParkingAdda parking guide to get directions, he will be available at the spot and help you park safely and securely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are a few simple safety guidelines to help you stay safe while getting in and out of your car,  with ParkingAdda’s guide a lot of these will be taken off & will help you park stress-free -</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Driver Safety</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Always keep track of where you parked, you’ll not have a ParkingAdda map or call guide.</li>\r\n <li>Avoid parking near shrubs or vans with slide-open doors on the side. When you park with us we mark and ensure space restrictions around your vehicle.</li>\r\n <li>Keep an eye out for strange people or activity in your immediate vicinity. ParkingAdda parking guide takes care of it.</li>\r\n <li>Keep your valuables in a place that is not directly visible from outside the vehicle. Stay safe don’t invite trouble.</li>\r\n <li>Basics! Once inside the vehicle, lock the doors and roll up the windows.</li>\r\n <li>Park as near to your building as possible in a well-lit and conspicuous location. The stress behind the same will be taken off by our 24x7 available spot representative.</li>\r\n <li>In poor weather, slow down. Take it easy! Follow the speed restriction limit.</li>\r\n <li>Be aware of automobiles and pedestrians when backing out.</li>\r\n <li>Keep an eye out for tiny children and parents with strollers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Parking lots in terms of Pedestrian Protection</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Vehicles have blind spots, so don&#39;t assume drivers can see. Take decisions to stay safe yourself.</li>\r\n <li>Wearing headphones or being distracted by cell phone conversations is not a good idea.</li>\r\n <li>In case your lost is huge parking lots, carry a whistle or another form of personal alarm.</li>\r\n <li>For entry, look around, inside, and underneath your vehicle. If you&#39;re suspicious, get out of there.</li>\r\n <li>Before you walk, take a look in both directions.</li>\r\n <li>At all times, be mindful of your surroundings, any vehicles speeding and stay mostly on the sides.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ParkingAdda is more than just vehicle safety</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from vehicle safety after it’s parked, ParkingAdda overall looks at solving the huge traffic and parking issues. We provide end to end parking solutions which means, instead of hustling at the last moment in search of parking, we provide an option for drivers to book a parking spot at any destination up to 36 hours in advance. On booking through the app, the map will guide you exactly to the spot where there will be a dedicated representative for any other additional help. This will be beneficial mainly for the working community and professionals who travel regularly for meetings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also try to make the most of any available space by offering the option to \"rent your place\" and earn money. There are many parking spots or unused spaces of land that lie vacant for quite a few hours during the day, we are trying to make use of these to meet the parking needs of the country. By ensuring space safety and passive income, land / parking owners will opt in to share their spaces. We developed our own proprietary technology and manufacture our own equipment in order to give a complete parking service. Any new or unexpected problems will or may come up can be easily resolved. In a nutshell, ParkingAdda manages all of its technology operations and manufacturing processes in-house. The way forward is to solve traffic problems with smart online parking solutions, which is why ParkingAdda is a need-based service in the country that organizes parking options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Avoid Parking and Vehicle Safety Issues with ‘ParkingAdda’.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What you need to do to get ‘ParkingAdda’?</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>The ParkingAdda Mobile App is available on the Google Play Store and the Apple App Store.</li>\r\n <li>You can use the app to find nearby parking (parking near me based on current location) or to reserve</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Parking at a faraway place.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Parking spots will be available on real time basis on the app&#39;s search location (Current status of the spot whether booked, Not available or available)</li>\r\n <li>As soon as you see it available, you can reserve it.</li>\r\n <li>All payments must be done via the ParkingAdda app wallet. For additional information on whether or not this money is refundable, read the Cancellation Policies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '19-10-22', '', 'parking');

